{"html":"<p>It’s happening, it’s finally happening - After 3 years of hiatus, E3 is finally coming back as a physical event in 2023, and I can’t contain myself.</p>\n<p></p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1024px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 133.203125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"Me while writting this post\" title=\"Me while writting this post\" src=\"/static/0e93743a85e03fab3fe678df24268bce/63217/e3_selfie.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/0e93743a85e03fab3fe678df24268bce/db830/e3_selfie.jpg 256w,\n/static/0e93743a85e03fab3fe678df24268bce/8102f/e3_selfie.jpg 512w,\n/static/0e93743a85e03fab3fe678df24268bce/63217/e3_selfie.jpg 1024w,\n/static/0e93743a85e03fab3fe678df24268bce/d58d1/e3_selfie.jpg 1536w,\n/static/0e93743a85e03fab3fe678df24268bce/09658/e3_selfie.jpg 2048w,\n/static/0e93743a85e03fab3fe678df24268bce/869dc/e3_selfie.jpg 2464w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Me while writting this post</figcaption>\n  </figure><p></p>\n<p>A few months ago it was the 10 years anniversary of my first E3, and <a href=\"/en/blog/games/10-years-anniversary-of-my-first-e3/\">I extensively wrote about all my experience</a> with past events and why I think we still need E3.</p>\n<p>My main reason was that a focused event with all major game announcements induces hype in everyone, and although you <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don%27t_Believe_the_Hype\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">shouldn’t believe the hype</a>, in this case, the hype is good, it helps the games to reach a broader audience that otherwise wouldn’t.</p>\n<p>I know I’m right because Gamescom this year was simply E3 but in Europe. I was even planning to go there this year, but I thought it wouldn’t be as nice to go myself, etc, and I canceled my plans, and now I regret it miserably.</p>\n<p>ANYWAY</p>\n<p>So when is E3 happening?</p>\n<h2 id=\"the-dates\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#the-dates\" aria-label=\"the dates permalink\" class=\"post-headers-link before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The dates</h2>\n<p>E3 2023 will happen from June 13th till June 16th, four days after the event for the first time - at least in the 10 years, I’ve been attending it.</p>\n<p>Not only that but two of these four days will be dedicated to media press and business, something that ESA probably learned from Gamescom.</p>\n<p>The two other days, called “Gamer Days”, will be open to the public, and you will be able to buy your tickets soon.</p>\n<p>I already updated my <a href=\"https://pablo.gg/en/e3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">E3 Countdown</a> page with the update dates. A bit more than 8 months for the best videogames event ever. Can’t wait!!</p>\n<p>See you guys there!</p>","path":"/en/blog/games/e3-2023-dates-revealed/","title":"E3 2023 dates revealed","language":"en","postHashId":"Z2FtZXN0cnVlbnVsbDIwMjItMDktMjdUMDA6MDA6MDAuMDAwWg==","comments":[],"relatedPosts":[{"path":"/en/blog/games/10-years-anniversary-of-my-first-e3/","postHashId":"Z2FtZXN0cnVlbnVsbDIwMjItMDYtMDFUMDA6MDA6MDAuMDAwWg==","title":"10 years anniversary of my first E3","date":"2022-06-01T00:00:00.000Z"},{"path":"/en/blog/events/e3-2012-and-here-we-go/","postHashId":"ZXZlbnRzdHJ1ZS4uLy4uL2NvdmVycy8yMDEyL3Bvc3QtaWQtMjIyMS1jb3Zlci5wbmcyMDEyLTA1LTMxVDAwOjAwOjAwLjAwMFo=","title":"E3 2012 - And here we... Go","date":"2012-05-31T00:00:00.000Z"},{"path":"/en/blog/games/metroid-5-is-finally-announced-19-years-later/","postHashId":"Z2FtZXN0cnVlbnVsbDIwMjEtMDYtMTZUMDA6MDA6MDAuMDAwWg==","title":"Metroid 5 is finally announced, 19 years later","date":"2021-06-16T00:00:00.000Z"},{"path":"/en/blog/events/trip-to-la-e3-2014/","postHashId":"ZXZlbnRzdHJ1ZS4uLy4uL2NvdmVycy8yMDE0L3Bvc3QtaWQtMjI2Ni1jb3Zlci5wbmcyMDE0LTA4LTA4VDAwOjAwOjAwLjAwMFo=","title":"Trip to LA - E3 2014","date":"2014-08-08T00:00:00.000Z"},{"path":"/en/blog/events/trip-to-e3-2012/","postHashId":"ZXZlbnRzdHJ1ZS4uLy4uL2NvdmVycy8yMDEyL3Bvc3QtaWQtMjIzMy1jb3Zlci5wbmcyMDEyLTEyLTIwVDAwOjAwOjAwLjAwMFo=","title":"Trip to E3 2012","date":"2012-12-20T00:00:00.000Z"},{"path":"/en/blog/tips/softwares-law-in-brazil/","postHashId":"dGlwc3RydWUuLi8uLi9jb3ZlcnMvMjAxMC9wb3N0LWlkLTE3NDMtY292ZXIucG5nMjAxMC0wMS0yNFQwMDowMDowMC4wMDBa","title":"Softwares law in Brazil","date":"2010-01-24T00:00:00.000Z"},{"path":"/en/blog/games/how-to-load-assets-asynchronously-with-phaser-3/","postHashId":"Z2FtZXN0cnVlbnVsbDIwMjEtMTEtMThUMDA6MDA6MDAuMDAwWg==","title":"How to load assets asynchronously with Phaser 3","date":"2021-11-18T00:00:00.000Z"},{"path":"/en/blog/games/buy-metroid-dread/","postHashId":"Z2FtZXN0cnVlbnVsbDIwMjEtMTEtMDdUMDA6MDA6MDAuMDAwWg==","title":"Buy Metroid Dread","date":"2021-11-07T00:00:00.000Z"},{"path":"/en/blog/coding/i-made-a-top-down-game-version-of-my-blog-with-phaser-and-react/","postHashId":"Y29kaW5ndHJ1ZW51bGwyMDIxLTEwLTEyVDAwOjAwOjAwLjAwMFo=","title":"I made a top-down game version of my blog with Phaser and React","date":"2021-10-12T00:00:00.000Z"},{"path":"/en/blog